comments: She is a hilarious teacher and very realistic about her demands as far as assignments and tests, making her class so enjoyable! One of the best classes ever!!!

Dr. Davis is THE best teacher I\'ve ever had. Great sense of humor, and makes you interested in the information. Tests for me were take home and open book, only 3-4 pg paper. Take Lifespan with her! She\'s awesome!

Tracy Davis has been the best teacher I\'ve had here hands down. She is incredibly knowlegable, funny as hell, and understand the demands of students. If you ever have to take a psych class, take her. You will NOT regret it. I miss her class already.

Seriously one of my favorite teachers at Augie! She is so funny and keeps the whole class entertained throughout the whole 2 hour class. The best part though is that I learned so much while having fun. She cares about how much you learn, not grades. She is super amazing! Take her Lifespan class! Hopefully, she will become a full time Augie teacher.
She was incredibly helpful and entertaining in class. A professor that can keep a class entertained for two hours straight is a great professor.

Dr. Davis is so awesome! She\'s wicked funny, but all of her jokes tie into what she is teaching. Her humor helps you b/c you\'re able to remember things better. Tests are sorta hard, but doable. You actually want to go to class bc its fun&she\'s very helpful w/your papers.She\'s probably my favorite teacher ever! Take this class- its wicked awesome!
Super funny and easy ot pay attention to.
